These are the licenses, that are used in "GTA2: Hacker's Remix":


- GPLv2 (or higher)
	for source code ('Makefile', 'src'-folder)

- CC-BY-4.0
	for artwork ('data'-folder)


Inside both the 'src' and 'data' folders is a 'LICENSE' file, that
contains the legal text of each license. The file 'data/AUTHORS'
lists all artwork authors. A human readable summary of the CC-BY-4.0
license is here: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

If you have any questions about the licensing, please ask here:
https://github.com/Bytewerk/gta2-hackers-remix/issues
